* Ukraine
by the numbers: Earlier this week, during the commercial break for Kasie Hu=
nt=E2=80=99s new CNN show, my fellow panelist Kristen Soltis Anderson share=
d a poll with me. Anderson, the co-founder of Echelon Insights, a Republica=
n-leaning polling firm that partners with Puck, pointed me to data indicati=
ng that American support for Ukraine has gotten squishy over time. In Octob=
er 2022, eight months into the war, 44 percent of Americans felt that our =
