ong>Kristen McDonald Rivet</strong>, <strong>Haley Stevens</strong>, and<st=
rong> Hillary Scholten</strong>, and former gubernatorial candidate and cur=
rent Wayne County health director <strong>Abdul El-Sayed </strong>are among=
